latestPosts.caption:
Shining bright on the red carpet My baby’s moment to shine, @aasthagill 💞✨I’m honored to be by her side always and forever🥹❤️

#RedCarpet #cannes

Here’s a lil story on how dreams are manifested and how they come alive!
I went to Inorbit mall with my friend and we were walking past the colorbar store adoring @jacquelienefernandez and her makeup and I told my friend I wish I could do her makeup one day to which he told you will do it sooner than you know it. It was t even one complete week when @shaanmu texted me asking if I would like to do @jacquelienefernandez makeup? For a second, I was totally dumbfounded until @shaanmu hello, you there? I was very much there and at the same time at cloud number infinity. 
Alas, the picture you see here is my dream come true! 
Thanks is a very small word to express my gratitude but a whole hearted thanks to @jacquelienefernandez and @shaanmu for bestowing this opportunity on me and believing in my talent. All an artist desires is to be validated and you did that for me. 
Much Love ❤️ 
#jacklinefernandez ❤️
